ram will allow you to create attractive photo albums to share with friends, don’t expect a lot of multimedia capability.","This software has an attractive, modern interface and a generous selection of free, pre-designed templates you can edit to your liking, with a variety of themes like birthdays and graduation. However, unlike the other products in our Mac digital scrapbook reviews, this software doesn’t connect to a marketplace to offer a selection of additional templates. This is a significant limitation, given that the other software packages have thousands of template options that you can pay for in addition to the free templates.","This software didn’t install quite as easily as the best digital software we tested for Mac. It took nearly 23 minutes to install, which was the second slowest. Once it was installed, it lacked the ease of use of the top software. The graphic interface on the other software in our lineup made it easy to find the tools we needed, but that was lacking with this program. Along with its lack of a searchable graphics feature, this software won’t automatically place photos on the page, so you will have to do all the photo arranging yourself. You may want to do that anyway, but having the option of auto-placement is always nice.","Support options are also somewhat limited with this software. You can access FAQs and online tutorials through the company’s website, but the only way to get answers to questions is via email. There are no forums for sharing information with other users online or telephone support."]},"id":"0934135b-bbee-468a-821f-d68ecc46264b","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"38677fb1-bda5-4194-9024-c3a274c9e067","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Scrapbook Crafter is quality software with plenty of free, pre-designed template options that will allow you to create a variety of photo albums you can share with friends. It has great editing tools to alter photos and give a unique look to your designs. But, unfortunately, you won’t be able to purchase additional templates through this software. While the photo editing tools are easy to use, the interface lacks navigational prowess. This software also won’t allow you to add multimedia elements to your photo album. Overall, it’s a valid, affordable option, but you won’t get the same versatility as the top software out there."]},"id":"84af99dc-207d-4650-a4fa-43ccc2ce69e7","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_67551","url":"/scrapbook-crafter-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"rebecca-spear","url":"/author/rebecca-spear","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Rebecca Spear","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"X8Ccy4LP9pMXtXdurbSshX","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2016-01-08T21:18:08Z","datePublished":"2016-01-08T21:18:08Z","name":"Scrapbook Crafter 1.0.0","synopsis":"Scrapbook Crafter is affordable Mac digital scrapbooking software with a lot of impressive features to recommend it. This software has a number of high quality editing tools and sharing options that make it a valuable tool for social media scrapbookers, but it has its limitations.","review":{"rating":69,"verdict":"Although it loses points for overall ease of use and versatility, Scrapbook Crafter is a great affordable option. ","pros":["Scrapbook Crafter will let you effectively edit photos before you post them on social media."],"cons":["This software doesn&#8217;t offer additional pre-designed template options through an online marketplace."]},"strapline":"Scrapbook Crafter is affordable Mac digital scrapbooking software with a lot of impressive features to recommend it. This software has a number of high quality editing tools and sharing options that make it a valuable tool for social media scrapbookers, but it has its limitations.","language":"en","dateModified":"2016-01-08T21:18:08Z","id":"CBwwCTehUfLVZhVY8goM7h","meta":{"title":"Scrapbook Crafter 